/* Creator: Fridan99
 * Colaborators: thatlonelybugbear, thx for the CSS part
 * Create a sript macro, then paste the code 
 * This will create a dialog window with buttons for each 5e Skills 
 * You can select a skill and see a printout to the chat 
 * Some minor things are modified, such as the actor endowment that instead of advantage in Deception, gives it in Performance, following the UA of the D&D One Direct.
 * Added some imprvements when proficient, and improvement of the Medicine skill to make it more useful.
 */

